# Steps to install SASS

1. Navigated to the project folder:
   cd alx-intermediate-frontend
   mkdir 0x03-sass_scss
   cd 0x03-sass_scss

2. Installed Node Version Manager (nvm):
   curl -o- https://raw.githubusercontent.com/nvm-sh/nvm/v0.39.7/install.sh | bash

3. Closed and reopened the terminal, then installed Node.js v20.16:
   nvm install 25.1.0
   nvm use 20.16

4. Checked versions:
   node -v
   npm -v

5. Installed SASS version 3.7.4 using npm:
   npm install sass -v 3.7.4
   11.6.2

6. Verified installation:
   npx sass --version
